          <td class="post-content">
            <div class="post-content-inner">
              
              Definitely more in the science fiction side than the high fantasy side. Aside from the examined and consistent future technology, the trans-humanism themes examine the concepts of noticeable evolution. The only time I saw fantasy explore this theme was Tomas of the Riftwar Saga, but that was magically-induced change into something that already was... A lot of the trans-humanism in Dune is to become something completely new.

              

              
              
